{"tid":2165991,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"『荔/長/深 三區撚入』是靚午 FAST TASTE","createTime":"2020-08-20T07:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T14:12:21.000Z","uid":310853,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"74165df58737e4b69400d62ca18f104b4f59e7d8","tid":2165991,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:07:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的 話說有日見有位巴打留言<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UjiTHKs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUjiTHKs.jpg&h=4c531992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再加上有個post係講佢 所以今日就去咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又一黃店被藍業主搞散家庭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2162645\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2162645</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fCF3kwB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfCF3kwB.png&h=e4d02e3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rf3wuqe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frf3wuqe.png&h=56295abc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Ou7Ncg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Ou7Ncg.png&h=e762129c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尾端有少少黑松露 不過唔算多<br />\n所以黑松露個味唔濃<br />\n個包同其他西式漢堡包一樣 都係大大個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n味道係OK嘅 幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3JucdTf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3JucdTf.png&h=ecaf31b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食到一半大約係咁嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FZhk7eC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFZhk7eC.png&h=c4efc2f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後我有加個魷魚鬚食<br />\n粉就重手咗少少 不過入面條魷魚鬚都幾大舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n地址就如下<br />\n價錢係有少少高 但我揀嗰個係和牛漢堡<br />\n同埋食親d大大份嘅漢堡包其實都係咁上下價錢<br />\n同埋依加有九折<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K3u7Nfp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK3u7Nfp.png&h=22f307ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我又再經歷多次 點解唔要嘢飲依個話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e25f78d578f937cafa761cc77e82727fd638689","tid":2165991,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:09:40.000Z","msg":"你有俾機會我叫佢咩"},{"pid":"fcee87cd2df7a65bd4085deb56189fc00e044054","tid":2165991,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e25f78d578f937cafa761cc77e82727fd638689","tid":2165991,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:09:40.000Z","msg":"你有俾機會我叫佢咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b247e8172ba2b9f8caf3d5aabe29a2fde0fa376","tid":2165991,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:11:35.000Z","msg":"我要長沙灣手足外送呀！唔要panda 呀"},{"pid":"5c000c9c479ee930280d4222628cb1b86cf77858","tid":2165991,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b247e8172ba2b9f8caf3d5aabe29a2fde0fa376","tid":2165991,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:11:35.000Z","msg":"我要長沙灣手足外送呀！唔要panda 呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:14:44.000Z","msg":"我都係特登行去買<br />\n但個位置其實有少少偏僻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n元州商場再入兩三條街 不過算易搵"},{"pid":"0f8a155bf64788b24da65c029d25f7a7d84b36e1","tid":2165991,"uid":13361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gi